@chapter Installation

Guilecraft is available for download from its website at
@url{http://guilecraft.somewhere/}.  This section describes the software
requirements of Guilecraft, as well as how to install it and get ready
to use it.

The build procedure for Guilecraft is the same as for other GNU software, and
is not covered here.  Please see the files @file{README} and
@file{INSTALL} in the Guilecraft source tree for additional details.

