@node Requirements
@section Requirements

Guilecraft depends on the following packages:

@itemize
@item @url{http://gnu.org/software/guile/, GNU Guile}, version 2.0.5 or later;
@item @url{http://gnupg.org/, GNU libgcrypt}
@end itemize

In addition, if you want to run the standard Guilecraft web client (UI)
then you'll need to install Artanis.  A version comes bundled with
Guilecraft, and it can be installed by simply copying it to the usual
Guile site directory. See below for getting the web client up and
running.

